headline: Cadence Delivers Enterprise-Level Reliability with Next-Gen Low-Power DRAM for AI Applications Featuring Microsoft RAIDDR ECC Technology
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., January 13, 2026--Cadence's LPDDR5X 9600Mbps memory IP system solution is designed specifically for enterprise and data center applications with high reliability.
